{"tid":1002562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海底撈與百度鬧笑話 將請勿收台譯成do not accept Taiwan","createTime":"2019-01-31T04:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T08:13:46.000Z","uid":89543,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a62c1147583fbc6a724f68d5bd93c477ef4bc5","tid":1002562,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國知名連鎖火鍋業者「海底撈」與搜尋引擎「百度」鬧笑話，竟將「請勿收台」的英文逐字翻譯成「do not accept Taiwan」，中國網友對此崩潰大罵「到底是太智能還是太弱智」<br />\n<br />\n根據《新浪科技》報導，近期內中國網友發現海底撈提供給客人使用的告示牌出現錯誤，1張提醒服務人員不用清理桌面的告示牌，英文翻譯竟為「do not accept Taiwan（請不要接受台灣）」，但海底撈並非唯一鬧笑話的，中國網友還指控搜尋引擎「百度」的翻譯功能也出錯。<br />\n<br />\n實際使用「百度翻譯」，在欄位中輸入「請勿收台」，竟然顯示出「Please do not accept Taiwan」，但按照這句話在中國的意思，正確翻譯應為「Please don't clean up the table（請勿收拾桌子）」，具有翻譯功能的其他搜尋引擎均未出此錯誤，讓中國網友相當不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n中國微博網友們甚至懷疑海底撈、百度的「政治立場」值得懷疑，不過，這張告示牌的照片在中國網域迅速被官方遮蔽；網友們留言指出「百度就是條狗」、「最近是要整百度呢？」、「抵制百度」，但也有網友認為「請勿收台是哪國中文？」、「這幾個字根本讀不通」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpj9Dxka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpj9Dxka.jpg&h=856a7db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpvFRXeE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpvFRXeE.jpg&h=41e9c670&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0117dcdeb4622e372943edafd5d31a21427e3a3a","tid":1002562,"uid":89543,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"百度加埋please<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299c3f420b74d48cc51cc1242a43a34c2aca62bb","tid":1002562,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0117dcdeb4622e372943edafd5d31a21427e3a3a","tid":1002562,"uid":89543,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"百度加埋please<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"唔夠位"},{"pid":"e0128131f973348ebeb8f82c10d20ba028f3739e","tid":1002562,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624d87b2dcb1c760aaa7f52a2f67a170dbc90302","tid":1002562,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:54:32.000Z","msg":"台獨份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c3c98a8dbce634097f2e3ae2b677c4b878a250","tid":1002562,"uid":33429,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:56:14.000Z","msg":"認真，打句縮寫完有歧義嘅句子入去再賴翻譯得唔準係咩玩法"},{"pid":"bb1870e6077c7ee3e416dcf125a3295ce0542b5f","tid":1002562,"uid":75823,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"唔好收枱係好正常既粵語"},{"pid":"b60702b809f05e8cdfe2442d5aa4a00e66e081ea","tid":1002562,"uid":117276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"do not accept Hong kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1257a8685e04bfd440ca82b96a5edb4faf31a14c","tid":1002562,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5c3c98a8dbce634097f2e3ae2b677c4b878a250","tid":1002562,"uid":33429,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:56:14.000Z","msg":"認真，打句縮寫完有歧義嘅句子入去再賴翻譯得唔準係咩玩法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"&gt;具有翻譯功能的其他搜尋引擎均未出此錯誤 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0190e208b8a3166bc8db36d7ddaf19b764d79638","tid":1002562,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:04:52.000Z","msg":"